<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/qna_detail.css">
  <title>QnA KU해</title>
</head>

<body>

  <%-include('top_bar.ejs')%>

  <header>
    <h1>QnA 상세페이지</h1>
  </header>

  <section>
    <div class="qna-box">
      <h3>업데이트 언제까지인가요?</h3>
      <p class="detail-info">
        작성자: <span>사용자1</span> | 날짜: <span>2023-11-23</span>
      </p>
      <div class="content">
        22일 시작하는 업데이트는 언제까지인가요?
      </div>
      <div class="button-container">
        <button class="back-button" onclick="goToListPage()">목록으로</button>
        <button class="edit-button" onclick="showEditForm()">수정</button>
        <button class="delete-button" onclick="confirmDelete()">삭제</button>
      </div>

      <div class="edit-form">
        <textarea id="edit-title" placeholder="제목"></textarea>
        <textarea id="edit-content" placeholder="내용"></textarea>
        <button class="save-button" onclick="saveChanges()">저장</button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="qna-box">
      <h3>업데이트 마감 날짜</h3>
      <div class="content">
        업데이트는 23일 23시까지 진행 예정입니다.
      </div>
      <div class="button-container">
        <button class="edit-button" onclick="goToEditAnswer()">수정</button>
        <button class="delete-button" onclick="confirmDeleteAnswer()">삭제</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <p>© KU-HAE</p>
  </footer>

  <script>
    function showEditForm() {
      const editForm = document.querySelector('.edit-form');
      editForm.style.display = 'block';
    }

    function saveChanges() {
      const editedTitle = document.getElementById('edit-title').value;
      const editedContent = document.getElementById('edit-content').value;

      const editForm = document.querySelector('.edit-form');
      editForm.style.display = 'none';

    }
  </script>

</body>

</html>
